```plantuml
@startuml zoolhelmy_ESP8266-Weather-Station

actor User

participant "ESP8266 NodeMCU" as ESP8266
participant "MQTT Broker" as MQTT
participant "ThingSpeak"
participant "OpenWRT Router" as OpenWRT
participant "GitHub Repository" as GitHub

User -> ESP8266: Trigger Data Acquisition

ESP8266 -> ESP8266: Gather Sensor Data

ESP8266 -> MQTT: Publish Data (MQTT)

MQTT -> ThingSpeak: Forward Data

MQTT -> OpenWRT: Forward Data

OpenWRT -> "mosquitto-subscribe.sh": Invoke Script

"mosquitto-subscribe.sh" -> "Temporary Files": Write Data

OpenWRT -> "collectd-rrdtool-publish.sh": Invoke Script

"collectd-rrdtool-publish.sh" -> "RRDTool Database": Update Database

OpenWRT -> "rrdtool-graph-github.sh": Daily Cron Job

"rrdtool-graph-github.sh" -> "RRDTool Database": Generate Graphs

"rrdtool-graph-github.sh" -> GitHub: Push Graphs

User -> ESP8266: Access Local HTTP Server

ESP8266 -> User: Display Real-time Readings

@enduml
```